# Task Dependencies API & Critical Path Method

This design document outlines the full-stack architecture required to implement PROMPT 1C, giving your system advanced Enterprise programmatic Project Management features (circular dependency protection, BullMQ Critical Path async computation).

## User Review Required

> [!CAUTION]
> Recursive PostgreSQL Queries (CTE) map strictly to Drizzle's `sql` literal helper. I will use native recursive RAW queries for speed and exact circular checking logic. 

